{
  "stem": "6762.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I, uh-- I start to get acquainted with the mayor from the city-- there was a small city there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I bought some tickets, bread tickets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I went to the store and buy maybe a couple kilos of bread and sold it on the black market.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And with this I could live a little bit to buy me some other food, whatever, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not a big deal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one day two agents, they caught me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I put the tickets in under my hat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] they took me under the arms, and they took the-- they took off the hat to find the tickets.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where did you get the tickets from?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, I found it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What can you say?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You cannot say, I bought it from the mayor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I told them I found it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they didn't believe me anyways.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They took me to the [NON-ENGLISH], to the police.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was the captain there, or whatever it was, a sergeant, whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he says, where you got the tickets from?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I said, I   found them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Throw him in jail.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Took off my shoelaces, you know, everything what you can-- and put me in jail.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Took away all the-- what I had-- a little bit  of money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Whatever I had, he took away, and he threw me in jail.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a few guys in jail already, but for different acts what they did.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was there-- they caught me  about 10:00 in the morning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was about a whole day almost.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they gave no food, no nothing, nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was lucky because those three guys had a girlfriend there through the window.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, the guy who were in the-- in the-- in the prison.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jail, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
